1
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:05,080
You don't hate me?

2
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,880
Chuntao's family has fallen apart.

3
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:09,840
That's why I managed to survive here.

4
00:01:10,039 --> 00:01:11,360
You're our benefactor.

5
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:12,320
I wouldn't dare.

6
00:01:12,360 --> 00:01:13,520
How would I dare to hate you?

7
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:16,640
Really?

8
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:19,160
I only like obedient people.

9
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:21,880
Miss, as long as you want,

10
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,920
I can do anything.

11
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:27,080
I'm willing to do anything.

12
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:29,360
Remember what you said today.

13
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:29,960
You may leave.

14
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:31,960
Yes.

15
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:37,560
The shop is simple.

16
00:01:37,759 --> 00:01:39,800
Did you rest well last night?

17
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:41,039
Not bad.

18
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,800
This is the best Longjing tea.

19
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:45,880
Please don't mind.

20
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,920
Why are you being so polite?

21
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,840
Just say it.

22
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:51,880
Okay.

23
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,640
I've thought about it.

24
00:01:54,479 --> 00:01:56,400
we should cancel our engagement.

25
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,560
We are not the only ones involved.

26
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,640
Are you determined?

27
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:03,880
Of course.

28
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:06,120
Your Highness.

29
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:07,920
I came here

30
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:09,160
to come here.

31
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:11,320
How dare you humiliate me like this?

32
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,840
It was my negligence.

33
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:15,760
If you feel ashamed,

34
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:18,000
you can pour all the dirty water on me.

35
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,280
When I return to the capital,

36
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:21,600
I'll personally visit Master Jiang and ask for forgiveness.

37
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:22,480
If you want to kill me,

38
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,520
as you wish.

39
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:26,200
You would rather die

40
00:02:26,440 --> 00:02:27,600
than marry me.

41
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,079
Xiao Wu Huo.

42
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,240
I've made up my mind.

43
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,240
You can stay

44
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:34,800
Please help yourself.

45
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,800
Chuntao.

46
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:48,200
Tell me what's wrong with me?

47
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,840
You look beautiful.

48
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,120
The Crown Prince must have lost his mind.

49
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,800
He will never betray us.

50
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:55,200
Traitor?

51
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:58,240
He was forced to marry me.

52
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,520
Even if he divorced Xu Sanniang,

53
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:03,080
she's still in my heart.

54
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,520
As long as she's here,

55
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,880
I'll always be the laughing stock in the capital.

56
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,600
Only when I die,

57
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,800
Rumors will be broken without destruction.

58
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,440
I am still the Crown Princess.

59
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:16,800
My Lady.

60
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,160
You can't do that.

61
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,280
How dare you disobey me again?

62
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:35,840
I can't.

63
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,960
What if it were you?

64
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:41,480
You said you would do anything

65
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,440
for me?

66
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,560
But that is the general conferred by His Majesty.

67
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,600
General.

68
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:51,560
She's just a loser.

69
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:55,240
Snake, insects, insects and insects often occur here.

70
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,960
General Xu can't take care of himself.

71
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:00,520
It's possible that he was poisoned and died.

72
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:09,400
Go. Show me your loyalty.

73
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,800
You're here.

74
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,680
This is the food and wine I prepared.

75
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,200
If you don't mind,

76
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:31,440
you can come with me.

77
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:32,720
No need.

78
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,400
The dishes are not your favourite.

79
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,400
I won't go with you.

80
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:38,400
You're so considerate.

81
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:40,320
He even remembers what he likes to eat.

82
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,600
He doesn't remember what I like to eat.

83
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,440
But I don't like

84
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:45,880
I don't like it.

85
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,720
Don't worry.

86
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:51,040
I prepared to leave.

87
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,520
Sorry for bothering you these days.

88
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:55,040
I apologize.

89
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:57,880
Then I'll eat it cute.

90
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:04,440
Yes.

91
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:08,280
But he has a bad stomach today.

92
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,320
He shouldn't drink.

93
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:12,240
I'll drink it for him.

94
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:14,280
Thank you for the meal.

95
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,600
Just so-so.

96
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,480
I'm going to help Suqin.

97
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,280
Come back tonight.

98
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,080
I'll send you there.

99
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,320
I've made it clear with Jiang Yingying.

100
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,280
She'll leave the day after tomorrow.

101
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,320
You can rest assured now.

102
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:48,320
The prince is so charming.

103
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:50,680
Who knows if someone else will come again?

104
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:54,040
I swear I'll only have you in my life.

105
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,000
If not,

106
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:58,000
I won't be able to die.

107
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,680
What are you talking about?

108
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:01,920
I'm telling the truth.

109
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:03,520
You're not angry anymore, right?

110
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:10,120
In your heart, I'm a grumpy woman

111
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,920
who doesn't listen to your explanation.

112
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,600
You're rude.

113
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:16,120
Sometimes she beats you.

114
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,120
Unlike her.

115
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:21,120
She's a daughter.

116
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,200
Of course.

117
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:27,320
A fair lady is a gentleman.

118
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,280
Why are you laughing?

119
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:37,360
I'm laughing.

120
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:41,120
The invincible Xu Sanniang

121
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,880
would be jealous for me.

122
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,040
Who will be jealous?

123
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:50,920
You don't have to be a lady.

124
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,600
I'm not a gentleman.

125
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,280
It's more important

126
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,280
is more important than anything.

127
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:11,520
What are you doing?

128
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:13,920
What makes you so intoxicated?

129
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:15,960
It's all your fault.

130
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,800
Xiao Bai, how dare you!

131
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,600
Where did you get the sachet?

132
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:35,440
What kind of popular pattern is this fat goose?

133
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:37,200
These are mandarin ducks.

134
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:42,200
I knew it was for someone else

135
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:44,680
The sun is rising from the west.

136
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:47,240
You can embroider now.

137
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:50,200
These days, insects and ants are poisonous.

138
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:53,040
That nerd got bitten many times when he was studying.

139
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,920
He values love over friendship.

140
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,440
Why don't you care about me?

141
00:07:57,600 --> 00:08:00,680
I'll embroider a fat goose for you too.

142
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:03,520
I don't want to wear the same sachet as you two.

143
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,880
I can't stand it.

144
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:13,320
I'm not going back.

145
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:18,120
I underestimated Xiao Bai.

146
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:20,160
He gave up his identity for you.

147
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,600
How dare you disobey my order? Eunuch Jiang.

148
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,640
Don't talk about us.

149
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:27,080
What about you?

150
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,240
You're old enough to get married.

151
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,880
Do you have someone you like?

152
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,840
I don't want to get married.

153
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:37,440
I just want to practice medicine to save people.

154
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:39,640
and help the people in Gusu County.

155
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,720
There is insecticide in it.

156
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:48,320
Yes, why?

157
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:51,280
By the way, a woman came to buy it this afternoon.

158
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:53,200
I should buy more then.

159
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,800
It's hot these days.

160
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,120
The ants are raw.

161
00:08:58,480 --> 00:08:59,640
It should be prepared often.

162
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:02,680
Is General Xu here?

163
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:03,960
I'm Chuntao.

164
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,320
Come in.

165
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:18,440
General Xu, it's our fault.

166
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,400
I made some soup

167
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:20,400
and made desserts.

168
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,720
I want you to try it.

169
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:23,880
You made this?

170
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:29,320
What's with the scar on your hand?

171
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,400
It's okay.

172
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:32,600
I scratched it by accident.

173
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,400
Wait.

174
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:45,040
It's not good for a girl to have a scar on her arm.

175
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,600
This is a medicine to remove scars.

176
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:47,960
Take it.

177
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,000
No.

178
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,560
There's not much left.

179
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,840
Go and get some for her.

180
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,240
You know the location of the pharmacy?

181
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:59,480
Didn't you just buy insecticide this morning?

